Zee One, a channel on pay TV platform, StarTimes, is set to give viewers a treat this Valentine by dedicating the entire month of February to Bollywood fans with thematic movies and drama series. In a statement made available to Saturday Beats, Ejiro Okene, the Chief Executive Officer, DeepVision, the media buying representatives of Zee One in Nigeria said, “With romantic dramas, romantic series and romantic comedies, we will be speaking the language of love fluently this February. If your love language is quality time, then there is no better time and place to plan a date night right in front of your screen with Zee One any day this month.”